OL,3,CGovernment promises new measures to
OL,4,Ctackle 'honour-based abuse'
OL,6,FNew measures will be introduced to
OL,7,Ftackle so-called "honour-based" abuse,
OL,8,Fthe Government has announced.
OL,10,FHonour-based abuse (HBA) is motivated
OL,11,Fby the perception that a person has
OL,12,Fbrought shame to themselves, their
OL,13,Ffamily or the community.
OL,15,FRelated crimes include female genital
OL,16,Fmutilation, forced marriage and murder.
OL,18,FNew statutory guidance and a legal
OL,19,Fdefinition of honour-based abuse will
OL,20,Fbe brought in to help combat the
OL,21,Fcrime, the government has said.
