OL,3,CGovernment promises new measures to
OL,4,Ctackle 'honour-based abuse'
OL,6,FThe Home Office will pilot a study
OL,7,Flooking at how widespread this crime
OL,8,Fis, a community awareness campaign
OL,9,Fwill be launched and teachers, police
OL,10,Fofficers, social workers and
OL,11,Fhealthcare professionals will receive
OL,12,Fmore training under the new policies.
OL,14,FThe measures have been backed by
OL,15,Fspecialist organisations targeting
OL,16,Fhonour-based abuse.
