OL,3,CGovernment promises new measures to
OL,4,Ctackle 'honour-based abuse'
OL,6,FIn 2021, pregnant Fawziyah Javed, 31,
OL,7,Fdied when she was pushed from Arthur's
OL,8,FSeat in Edinburgh by her husband after
OL,9,Fshe decided to leave the marriage. He
OL,10,Fwas jailed for life for her murder.
OL,12,FAfter Fawziyah's death, her mother
OL,13,FYasmin Javed teamed up with the
OL,14,Fcharity Karma Nirvana, which has been
OL,15,Fcalling on the government to introduce
OL,16,Fa legal definition for honour-based
OL,17,Fabuse.
