OL,3,CGovernment promises new measures to
OL,4,Ctackle 'honour-based abuse'
OL,6,F"As Fawziyah's mother, I am pleased
OL,7,Fthat the government has listened to
OL,8,Four calls for a statutory definition
OL,9,Fof honour-based abuse, and that this
OL,10,Fchange has been made in Fawziyah's
OL,11,Fmemory," Yasmin said.
OL,13,F"I hope that this will help many more
OL,14,Fpeople affected by HBA and ensure that
OL,15,Fthe multiple perpetrators of this
OL,16,Fabuse are properly recognised and
OL,17,Faddressed."
