OL,3,CGovernment promises new measures to
OL,4,Ctackle 'honour-based abuse'
OL,6,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,7,F"All forms of honour-based abuse are
OL,8,Fdevastating crimes that can shatter
OL,9,Flives. There is no 'honour' in them.
OL,11,F"For too long, these offences have
OL,12,Foften been misunderstood by
OL,13,Fprofessionals, resulting in victims
OL,14,Fnot getting the support they deserve.
