OL,6,F"Make no mistake ` we will use
OL,7,Feverything at our disposal to make
OL,8,Fsure perpetrators face justice and
OL,9,Fvictims are protected."
OL,11,FJess Phillips, minister for
OL,12,Fsafeguarding and violence against
OL,13,Fwomen and girls, said: "These crimes
OL,14,Fcan cause unimaginable, long-lasting
OL,15,Fphysical and mental pain for their
OL,16,Fvictims.
OL,18,F"They have no place in our society and
OL,19,Fwe must do everything we can to put a
OL,20,Fstop to them.
