OL,3,CGovernment promises new measures to
OL,4,Ctackle 'honour-based abuse'
OL,6,F"This starts with a clearer definition
OL,7,Fof the crime and guidance backed in
OL,8,Flaw so that the Government, law
OL,9,Fenforcement and the voluntary sector
OL,10,Fcan work hand-in-hand to give victims
OL,11,Fthe support they deserve.
OL,13,F"It is also vital that we understand
OL,14,Fthe true scale and nature of these
OL,15,Fcrimes in England and Wales.
OL,17,F"This will enable us and our partners
OL,18,Fto help make sure that more victims
OL,19,Fare protected and more perpetrators
OL,20,Fface time behind bars."
